Package org.universAAL.lddi.samples.device.client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activator
    Activator for Device Client sample bundle
    DeviceClient
    This is the connector class to the universAAL related ontology classes, mainly DeviceContextListener.java This class knows nothing about Ontologies! It could be part of a Java application.
    DeviceContextListener
    This class handles ontological context events by subscribing specific event patterns on the universAAL context bus This class is stateless; no objects (sensors) are stored here LogUtil from universAAL-Middleware is used here
    DeviceServiceCaller
    This class provides ontological service requests and processes the service responses This class is stateless; no objects (sensors) are stored here LogUtil from universAAL-Middleware is used here
